00:32:41,510 --> 00:32:42,300
This is great.

586
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:43,520
Thank you, Miss Man'er.

587
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:44,280
I look forward to working with you.

588
00:32:44,280 --> 00:32:44,810
Come on.

589
00:32:44,830 --> 00:32:45,670
This is great.

590
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:46,910
