741
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:14,310
Boss Wu.

742
00:39:14,610 --> 00:39:16,070
People call him Master Wu.

743
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:17,280
Master Wu decides

744
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,790
