788
00:41:31,210 --> 00:41:31,900
Honey,

789
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:34,040
you are so kind.

790
00:41:35,220 --> 00:41:36,460
Why didn't you tell me

791
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:38,030
