823
00:43:08,580 --> 00:43:10,310
something is bound to go wrong.

824
00:43:10,460 --> 00:43:11,790
It's best to be cautious

825
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:14,230
and make wine to save money for the shop.

826
00:43:15,500 --> 00:43:17,760
So, I still have to build up from nothing.

827
00:43:21,630 --> 00:43:22,620
What are you sewing?

828
00:43:22,620 --> 00:43:24,550
