829
00:43:25,350 --> 00:43:26,130
We've been staying here

830
00:43:26,130 --> 00:43:26,780
for a long time.

831
00:43:26,780 --> 00:43:27,530
I'll feel bad

832
00:43:27,560 --> 00:43:28,760
